	<ThingDef ParentName="TOT_WeaponsNoQuality">
        <defName>QBZ_fivenineFlame</defName>
        <label>&lt;color=#FFD456>AR-232F "Kirin"&lt;/color></label>
        <description>The AR-231F "Kirin" is an unofficial variant of the QBZ-231R assault rifle that adopts a more classic configuration while maintaining a high parts commonality. It is available exclusively through custom order from the C.A.G. In response to the harsh environments of border worlds, this configuration simplifies the precision electromagnetic rail assembly in favor of enhanced mechanical durability. However, this results in a slightly reduced effective range, longer heat dissipation cycles, lower accessory compatibility, and a conspicuous muzzle flash when fired.\n\nThis rifle is chambered for a specialized 6×36mm API round, which can ignite targets after penetration and cause secondary fire damage.</description>
